                        "AcquisitionStrategy": {
                            "val": "The acquisition, management, and contracting strategy involves the following:\n\u2022 Adhere to guidance outlined in DoD 5000, Directive 7, Federal Acquisition Regulations (FAR), and FAR Supplement Policies and Procedures.\n\u2022 Acquire and sustain SM&OIE capabilities, systems, tools, products, and services through a disciplined, yet agile, process that ensures information related capabilities are available for DoD components.\n\u2022 Sustain an acquisition process that is responsive and responsible to internal and external customers and stakeholders.\n\u2022 Continue to support the warfighter\u2019s need for capabilities that dominate today\u2019s dynamic, networked battlespace by providing governance, oversight, and strategy across the DoD for the planning and execution of SM&OIE activities."
